  "description": "Use this skill when building or debugging a custom Salesforce Commerce payment gateway adapter using the CommercePayments Apex namespace \u2014 covering adapter implementation, RequestType handling, PCI tokenization patterns, and integration path selection. NOT for billing (Salesforce Billing / blng namespace), NOT for configuring the legacy sfdc_checkout.CartPaymentAuthorize interface (see admin/commerce-checkout-configuration), and NOT for storefront UI payment form design.",
